{"tid":413463,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[哲學] 會唔會怕死亡個一刻？有冇後悔出世？","createTime":"2017-09-25T12:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T12:07:27.000Z","uid":91648,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e90a15cd517e3687a4dd5c2051bc270549b72373","tid":413463,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T12:38:45.000Z","msg":"見7月咁多人死，自己都開始思考死亡。有時會諗下死個一刻會點，會唔會好痛苦 ，透唔到氣好辛苦。有時一覺醒來，心想未死，但終有一日會死，個人會灰左一下。 世界上咩野都可以選擇去做或唔做，但死亡就係冇得揀。<br />\n<br />\n更重要係，人死左後，&ldquo;未來&quot;呢個詞語就唔在有意義，話你知宇宙千百億年咁耐先完結都係無意思，其實都係一貶眼就完，咁大家嘅出現真係好無聊。<br />\n<br />\nsry 1999.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85dae7377df24fa97403b44bc8a8c843b0194878","tid":413463,"uid":48631,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T12:44:55.000Z","msg":"生活得幸福既先怕死,我呢d廢柴唔會怕架"},{"pid":"50bfc742ae04182483ffddc559e35c07b584a64c","tid":413463,"uid":121409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:06:29.000Z","msg":"雖然唔算係活得精彩，但唔會有種自己想尋死或者覺得厭世ge心態<br />\n但如果你同我講我下一秒就會死我又冇咩野<br />\n活在當下，隨遇而安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d4ccb9134f8cf13e055c6a42865ac6e8aad9fe","tid":413463,"uid":137487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:12:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生活得幸福既先怕死,我呢d廢柴唔會怕架</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e3937f78f2b48bfbc0eec4cc3b1d898f97c714","tid":413463,"uid":99024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:14:33.000Z","msg":"怕"},{"pid":"005c8554516f06a2ee33e3aaae0250a9a12bc02a","tid":413463,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:18:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c004d460febb909b08392d5eee5c33b8b3fc12d","tid":413463,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:18:59.000Z"