連驚既時間都冇"},{"pid":"54063351c333e9ab27902114d6c9d4b2476cf7cd","tid":413463,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:54:52.000Z","msg":"七歲嗰陣睇過姨媽嗰啲講佛嘅錄影帶，見啲人火葬，嗰陣我諗到底我死咗使唔使好似佢咁燒到渣都冇？如果要嘅話我幾多歲先死，幾多歲之後要咁樣俾人燒屍？"},{"pid":"ab550251764255c8508fbfaf0db09544f9f9ecb1","tid":413463,"uid":34863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:54:53.000Z","msg":"依加嘅我哋好多人都會怕<br />\n我覺得當你老咗<br />\n慒慒下就唔會諗咁多呢啲問題<br />\n瓜咗都唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b812461d9bfde8c21e74333711a74d30d857e7","tid":413463,"uid":90457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:57:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>七歲嗰陣睇過姨媽嗰啲講佛嘅錄影帶，見啲人火葬，嗰陣我諗到底我死咗使唔使好似佢咁燒到渣都冇？如果要嘅話我幾多歲先死，幾多歲之後要咁樣俾人燒屍？</blockquote><br />\n嗰陣我仲係好幼稚，驚死驚到唔敢瞓，怕一覺之後就死咗，寧願自己多停留喺有意識嘅狀況，結果成兩晚冇教好瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb96355b067465a99b5950e6ddd97157de4f9744","tid":413463,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:59:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生活得幸福既先怕死,我呢d廢柴唔會怕架</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817c9ad5f7f2eb10fbc58ae5be36716f35e89f1a","tid":413463,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T12:07:27.000Z","msg":"推"}]}